blogs.title: Sunday Meeting!
blogs.body:
This sunday we have to scheduled a meeting at 2 o'clock in the morning. This is a very imp meeting and you should attend that as it will impact your career very greatly.
So I guess I'll see you at the meeting.
Till then take care.
blogs.author: yoshi
